{"type":"message","id":"e97ee9a5","parentId":"2888e5d6","timestamp":"2026-04-12T23:16:07.987Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:96581978-d878-4527-8afb-e74fcefebdc4 daily-ping-telegram] Send the daily ping to Telegram target 1087368827 with fresh data.\n\n**EXACT FORMAT REQUIRED:**\n\n🌅 Daily Ping — {DAY}, {MMM} {DD}, {YYYY}\n\n💰 Bitcoin\n• Price: ${BTC_PRICE} USD\n• 24h: {BTC_CHANGE}% {TREND}\n\n📊 Tech Stocks\n• NVDA: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• MSFT: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• GOOGL: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• INTC: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• META: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• AMD: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n\n📊 Market: S&P {SPX}, Nasdaq {NDX} — {BRIEF_COMMENTARY}\n\n🚀 Trending GitHub Repos (Created Since 2025)\n1. {repo} ⭐ {stars}K\n... (top 10)\n\n— ⏰ {HH}:{MM} SGT | Data: CoinGecko, Yahoo Finance, GitHub API\n\n**DATA TO FETCH:**\n\n1. Bitcoin: Use CoinGecko API (https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true)\n2. Stocks: Use Yahoo Finance API for: NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD\n3. Indices: S&P 500 (^GSPC) and Nasdaq Composite (^IXIC)\n4. GitHub: Search repos created since 2025-01-01, sort by stars, limit 10\n\n**TREND EMOJIS:** Use 📈 if positive, 📉 if negative, ➖ if ~0%\n\n**BRIEF_COMMENTARY:** Generate a 1-sentence market summary based on the data\n\nUse web_search and web_fetch to get the data, then message tool to send to Telegram.\nCurrent time: Monday, April 13th, 2026 - 7:15 AM (Asia/Singapore) / 2026-04-12 23:15 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776035767981}}
